data.description: Beautiful custom brick single family home. 5 bedrooms. 2 car plus golf cart space garage.  8 off street parking spaces. Full house Solar, QuartziteGranite on all cabinet counter surfaces. Self Contained Bonus efficiency Apartment above garage. Swimming with heat pump, heated pool. Indoor Plantation window shutters. High impact windows. Ceiling Fans, Enclosed swimming pool screened atrium with additional small RV parking space. Solar provides 95% of monthly $350 power bill. Apt above garage is 95% complete. Kitchen cabinets not complete. All else finished.
